bbcode_enabled = true
text = "[center][wave amp=25 freq=2][color=orange][font_size=26][b]Welcome to \"The Hamster Engine\"[/b][/font_size][/color][/wave][/center]

A brilliant (and perhaps slightly unhinged) scientist has nearly completed his greatest invention: the [color=lime][b]Pollution-nator[/b][/color]. Unfortunately, creating world-ending pollution requires an incredible amount of energy...

There was only one logical solution...

[center][rainbow][font_size=30][b]HAMSTERS!!![/b][/font_size][/rainbow][/center]

The first step is building a workforce. Hamsters can be purchased by clicking on an empty cage. Don't worry too much about where the starting energy came from... some questions are better left unanswered.
"
fit_content = true

