theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 12
theme_override_font_sizes/bold_font_size = 12
theme_override_font_sizes/bold_italics_font_size = 12
theme_override_font_sizes/italics_font_size = 12
theme_override_font_sizes/mono_font_size = 12
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "[center][color=yellow][b]Hamster Statistics[/b][/color][/center]

Hovering over a hamster reveals three important attributes:

[color=lightgreen][b]Stamina[/b][/color]
Determines how long a hamster can keep running before becoming exhausted.

[color=lightblue][b]Speed[/b][/color]
Determines how much power the hamster generates while running.

[color=tomato][b]Health[/b][/color]
Once stamina has been depleted, the hamster begins taking damage. If its health reaches zero... well... science requires sacrifices.

Hamsters can be dragged from their cages directly onto a wheel to begin generating power."
fit_content = true

