[node name="RichTextLabel" type="RichTextLabel" parent="MarginContainer3/Part3" unique_id=280165055]
layout_mode = 2
theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 12
theme_override_font_sizes/bold_font_size = 12
theme_override_font_sizes/bold_italics_font_size = 12
theme_override_font_sizes/italics_font_size = 12
theme_override_font_sizes/mono_font_size = 12
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "[center][color=yellow][b]Power Generation[/b][/color][/center]

As a hamster runs, its stamina gradually decreases while power production increases.

If your machine produces [color=lightgreen]more power than it consumes[/color], the excess energy is stored in the battery.

If consumption exceeds production, the battery slowly drains.

[color=red][b]If the battery is ever completely depleted, the Pollution-nator is destroyed, and the scientist's dreams go up in smoke.[/b][/color]
"
fit_content = true

