theme_override_font_sizes/mono_font_size = 12
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "[center][color=yellow][b]Machine Modules[/b][/color][/center]

Victory is achieved by completing all three [color=orange][b]Project Modules[/b][/color] located near the bottom of the machine.

Most modules in the first two rows provide new abilities or increase production, but every installed module also increases the machine's power requirements.

Expanding too quickly can leave the machine unable to sustain itself.

The first available module is the [color=cyan][b]Experimental Tank[/b][/color].

Hamsters placed inside are temporarily unavailable while mysterious scientific \"improvements\" are performed. When the process finishes, the hamster returns to an empty cage with one of its attributes randomly increased.

Whether those experiments are ethical is... outside the scope of this tutorial."
fit_content = true

