text = "[center][color=lime][font_size=24][b]Good luck![/b][/font_size][/color][/center]

Keep the hamsters healthy, expand the machine carefully, and generate enough power to complete the Pollution-nator.

The fate of the scientist's masterpiece now rests in the tiny paws of some very hardworking rodents"
